OL,3,CCouncil plans to ban junk food adverts
OL,4,Cin some public places
OL,6,FA Welsh council could soon be the
OL,7,Ffirst in the country to ban the
OL,8,Fadvertisement of unhealthy foods in
OL,9,Fcertain public spaces.
OL,11,FVale of Glamorgan Council announced it
OL,12,Fwill make a decision next month on the
OL,13,Fproposed ban which would stop foods
OL,14,Fcategorised as high in fat, sugar, and
OL,15,Fsalt being promoted at bus stops and
OL,16,Fon boards along the local authority's
OL,17,Froads.
