OL,6,F"As well as increasing economic,
OL,7,Feducation, and other opportunities
OL,8,Fthat pledge is about taking steps to
OL,9,Fimprove the health and wellbeing of
OL,10,Four residents and encouraging more
OL,11,Factive lifestyles.
OL,13,F"There is clear evidence that such
OL,14,Fadvertising contributes to people
OL,15,Fpurchasing and eating unhealthy foods
OL,16,Fand drinks, particularly children, and
OL,17,Fthat this in turn leads to higher
OL,18,Frates of obesity and other diet-
OL,19,Frelated diseases.
