OL,6,F"Research has also shown that those
OL,7,Fliving in areas of deprivation are the
OL,8,Fworst affected as advertising is often
OL,9,Fspecifically targeted at people living
OL,10,Fin those areas."
OL,12,FIn March 2025, the Senedd approved new
OL,13,Fregulations which will see
OL,14,Frestrictions placed on where retailers
OL,15,Fcan display certain unhealthy foods in
OL,16,Ftheir shops and on their websites.
OL,18,FThe new regulations, which will come
OL,19,Finto force next year, will also affect
OL,20,Ffoods which are high in sugar, fat,
OL,21,Fand salt.
